title: 20 Minute Full Body Strength Workout (No Equipment/No Repeat)
description:
Tap in with us for a 20 minute FULL BODY strength building workout that requires no equipment! This workout focuses on 'time under tension'---meaning each exercises will be performed slow and controlled to ensure your muscles are fully engaged. This is a great workout for beginners who want to build good overall strength with basic bodyweight exercises. For the more advanced, feel free to add resistance using dumbbells, kettlebells, or weight vest to make it more challenging. Give the workout a go and let us know how you did in the comments! 🔥

I love the fact that you guys use a sound to signify when you're switching sides during an exercise. You understand that we're not always looking at the screen. This is going to be my new go to workout for a while! Got my heart rate really up there and I feel like I really got a great workout in about 20 mins. AMAZING!!!

Thank you guys very much. I was in a motorcycle accident in 2018.
